    <h2>Smeg wall oven models we service</h2>
    <div class="model-grid">
      <div class="model-card"><h3>Victoria Series retro wall oven</h3><p>Signature Smeg retro aesthetic — curved door design, colorful finish options (pastel hues + bold Italian colors). Popular in design-forward Silver Lake + Los Feliz + West Hollywood kitchens. Service: aesthetic trim tier-specific.</p></div>
      <div class="model-card"><h3>Classic Series modernist wall oven</h3><p>Clean contemporary design language — more subdued than Victoria's retro emphasis. Competes at modernist kitchen aesthetic positioning. Shared mechanical platform with Victoria at component level.</p></div>
      <div class="model-card"><h3>Dolce Stil Novo premium wall oven</h3><p>Smeg's premium tier — upscale Italian design language, premium control platform, higher-end finish quality. Positions at the upper end of Smeg's wall oven lineup.</p></div>
      <div class="model-card"><h3>Interior mechanical service</h3><p>Bake element, convection fan, control board, sensors, door hardware. Largely interchange across Smeg tiers with tier-specific variants.</p></div>
      <div class="model-card"><h3>Victoria curved-door specialty</h3><p>Victoria's signature curved door design + colorful panel finishes require tier-specific parts chain. Glass door + aesthetic trim quoted individually.</p></div>
      <div class="model-card"><h3>Self-clean pyrolytic cycle</h3><p>Standard pyrolytic self-clean on current Smeg wall oven generations. Door-lock motor + thermal sensor + cycle firmware.</p></div>
    </div>
  </div></section>

